summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire land and other property necessary for the laying off, opening, widening and establishing of Olson Place Southwest and establishing an unnamed street connecting Olson Place Southwest and 4th Avenue Southwest under Ordinance 99278, King County Cause No. 741002; accepting a condemnation award (Parcel 5) in connection therewith; and making a reimbursable appropriation from the Arterial City Street Fund therefor.
